 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The antioxidant half-maximal inhibitory concentration (IC
  <sub>50</sub>) for each of the studied
  <span class="italic"> R. chalepensis</span> essential oils and Trolox and their standard deviations were calculated by using BioData Fit edition 1.02 (data fit for biologist).
 </p>
